}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The hub populating this entry is white. It's S/N is '''UN1308U271079'''.
"UH-07H-R012" is silkscreened on the bottom of the board. :A sticker with "102-12110081" and "1301000779" is also affixed to the board. The '''SMSC''' hub IC package is marked with "SMSC", "USB2507-ADT", "A1231-AC16", and "8R151588B". :It would appear that the manufacturer disabled MTT support.
The power adapter included with the device is a '''GOE''' GS2U-012-0502000-L / GS2J-012-0502000-L (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.5A -> 5VDC 2.0A).
The QIG included with the hub is dated 2011-12-08.
